caption: Small fenced park surrounded by Rue Jean-Baptiste Clement.
Just a triangle shaped flower garden in the middle of paradise.
Don't expect a park! It's basically a small patch of greenery, pleasant all the same. Between 2 roads and a pedestrian walkway, so not particularly quiet or pretty
While strolling around Montmartre, a flower garden suddenly appeared. The pretty flowers were blooming beautifully in the late summer sunlight.
